section#about.page-section
    .container
        .text-center
            h2.section-heading.text-uppercase(data-i18n='about.heading', data-en='About', data-zh='关于我们') About
            h3.section-subheading.text-muted(data-i18n='about.subheading', data-en='The milestones that shaped our studio and the way we work today.', data-zh='这些关键节点塑造了我们的团队，也定义了今天的工作方式。') The milestones that shaped our studio and the way we work today.
        ul.timeline
            li
                .timeline-image
                    img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/1.jpg', alt='...')
                .timeline-panel
                    .timeline-heading
                        h4 2009-2011
                        h4.subheading(data-i18n='about.item1.title', data-en='Our Humble Beginnings', data-zh='从小规模起步') Our Humble Beginnings
                    .timeline-body
                        p.text-muted(data-i18n='about.item1.text', data-en='We started with a small team, a simple mission, and a belief that thoughtful design can create real business value.', data-zh='我们从一个小团队开始，坚持用清晰的设计和可靠的交付，为客户创造真正的商业价值。') We started with a small team, a simple mission, and a belief that thoughtful design can create real business value.
            li.timeline-inverted
                .timeline-image
                    img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/2.jpg', alt='...')
                .timeline-panel
                    .timeline-heading
                        h4 March 2011
                        h4.subheading(data-i18n='about.item2.title', data-en='An Agency is Born', data-zh='品牌正式成立') An Agency is Born
                    .timeline-body
                        p.text-muted(data-i18n='about.item2.text', data-en='As our projects grew, we built a clearer process for strategy, design, development, and long-term partnership.', data-zh='随着项目不断增加，我们逐步建立了从策略、设计到开发与长期合作的完整流程。') As our projects grew, we built a clearer process for strategy, design, development, and long-term partnership.
            li
                .timeline-image
                    img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/3.jpg', alt='...')
                .timeline-panel
                    .timeline-heading
                        h4 December 2015
                        h4.subheading(data-i18n='about.item3.title', data-en='Transition to Full Service', data-zh='升级为全案服务') Transition to Full Service
                    .timeline-body
                        p.text-muted(data-i18n='about.item3.text', data-en='We expanded from visual execution into a full-service model covering content, systems, and digital touchpoints.', data-zh='我们从单纯的视觉执行，扩展到内容、系统与数字触点的整合式服务。') We expanded from visual execution into a full-service model covering content, systems, and digital touchpoints.
            li.timeline-inverted
                .timeline-image
                    img.rounded-circle.img-fluid(src='assets/img/about/4.jpg', alt='...')
                .timeline-panel
                    .timeline-heading
                        h4 July 2020
                        h4.subheading(data-i18n='about.item4.title', data-en='Phase Two Expansion', data-zh='第二阶段扩张') Phase Two Expansion
                    .timeline-body
                        p.text-muted(data-i18n='about.item4.text', data-en='By investing in stronger delivery and communication, we were able to support bigger launches and more complex work.', data-zh='通过加强交付能力与协作机制，我们开始支持更大型、更复杂的上线项目。') By investing in stronger delivery and communication, we were able to support bigger launches and more complex work.
            li.timeline-inverted
                .timeline-image
                    h4(data-i18n='about.cta', data-en='Be Part Of Our Story!', data-zh='欢迎加入我们的故事！')
                        | Be Part
                        br
                        | Of Our
                        br
                        | Story!
